Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:29.976 --> 00:00:31.565
First of all,

00:00:31.566 --> 00:00:34.700
it's a great honor to be
back at Santos FC,

00:00:35.118 --> 00:00:38.904
now in a different role
from the one I used to have,

00:00:39.258 --> 00:00:41.562
20, 30 years ago.

00:00:42.288 --> 00:00:43.870
It's a great honor,

00:00:43.871 --> 00:00:45.433
I'm very happy,

00:00:45.767 --> 00:00:49.697
especially to be able to work with
fellow workers...

00:00:49.698 --> 00:00:50.803
from different generations,

00:00:50.804 --> 00:00:53.433
such as Lima, Abel,

00:00:54.281 --> 00:00:55.857
NenÃª Belarmino and...

00:00:55.858 --> 00:00:57.039
Juary, who...

00:00:57.903 --> 00:01:01.041
were part of the remarkable
"Meninos da Vila" team.

00:01:01.319 --> 00:01:02.612
It's a great honor,

00:01:02.613 --> 00:01:03.712
but now I am
in a different position.

00:01:03.713 --> 00:01:05.002
Honestly,

00:01:05.003 --> 00:01:08.249
we did not expect their level
to be as good as it is,

00:01:08.804 --> 00:01:12.114
there are some soccer schools
that are doing a great job.

00:01:12.115 --> 00:01:14.168
Many places do not have
a soccer school,

00:01:14.169 --> 00:01:17.267
many cities do not have
a soccer school,

00:01:17.268 --> 00:01:18.786
we could go there
to check them out,

00:01:18.787 --> 00:01:21.380
and perhaps, with the help of God,
find new players.

00:01:21.610 --> 00:01:23.983
Our goal is to observe...

00:01:24.345 --> 00:01:27.767
the ones who have
all the characteristics...

00:01:27.768 --> 00:01:30.819
to be a professional player.

00:01:31.051 --> 00:01:32.592
Two categories were
evaluated in the morning,

00:01:32.825 --> 00:01:34.649
then we had to stop
due to the rain,

00:01:34.982 --> 00:01:36.490
and now, in the afternoon,
another two.

00:01:36.491 --> 00:01:39.089
I believe it's important because...

00:01:39.305 --> 00:01:42.221
they are seeing how it is like
to be a professional player,

00:01:42.222 --> 00:01:46.915
it's a completely different setup.

00:01:47.996 --> 00:01:49.208
I've been trying,

00:01:49.761 --> 00:01:51.414
I took part in several tryouts,

00:01:51.849 --> 00:01:53.080
and now I made it,

00:01:53.081 --> 00:01:54.299
I'm happy to be here

